---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>404 | Deepdots Popup SDK</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f6f8fb;
        --panel: #ffffff;
        --text: #102a43;
        --muted: #486581;
        --accent: #2cb1bc;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #d9f2f2, var(--bg) 45%);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      main {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .card {
        max-width: 720px;
        background: var(--panel);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.12);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 3rem;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        background: var(--accent);
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="card">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>La pagina que buscas no existe o ha cambiado de ruta.</p>
        <p>Vuelve a la documentacion principal para continuar.</p>
        <a href="/">Ir al inicio</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
